00:02:51.500 --> 00:02:56.533
The probability of A and B happening.

00:02:57.300 --> 00:02:59.300
A and B.

00:02:59.300 --> 00:03:00.933
I want to stay true to the colors.

00:03:01.100 --> 00:03:02.700
Is equal to ...

