00:03:57.670 --> 00:03:58.833
You multiply those together, you get the

00:03:58.833 --> 00:04:00.800
probability that both happened.

00:04:01.366 --> 00:04:03.600
So why is this helpful for us?

00:04:03.767 --> 00:04:05.833
Well, we know a lot of this information.

00:04:05.833 --> 00:04:10.660
We know the probability
of A given B is 0.7.

00:04:10.660 --> 00:04:12.700
So let me write that, I'll
