So we know that the probability of A and B

00:04:23.100 --> 00:04:24.800
is the product of these two things.

00:04:24.900 --> 00:04:29.666
That's going to be 0.35.

00:04:29.766 --> 00:04:32.166
Seven times five is 35
or, I guess you could say,

00:04:32.166 --> 00:04:35.333
